{"tid":1652111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於國難五金件事……","createTime":"2019-10-13T14:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T15:23:45.000Z","uid":254456,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b788d68887acdd5369d4367d34a55f127d00db05","tid":1652111,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:35:19.000Z","msg":"其實我真係唔明你哋喺度屌緊啲乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國難五金老細賣唔賣裝備<br />\n<br />\n關你哋咩事？<br />\n<br />\n有人屌佢小學雞<br />\n<br />\n你冇返佢咁上下財力同資源唔該你哋唔好屌佢<br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句<br />\n<br />\n人哋老鳳買Gear畀你㗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>問題嚟喇</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你係咪一定要有佢Gear先生存到？<br />\n<br />\n如果係<br />\n<br />\n咁你仲屌佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係<br />\n<br />\n咁你理得佢哋開唔開舖啫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可能會問<br />\n<br />\n佢市場佔有率幾多<br />\n<br />\n我答你唔到<br />\n<br />\n但係大家都見到<br />\n<br />\n國難五金再開番<br />\n<br />\n再有學生價嗰一日<br />\n<br />\n條隊轉咗三個彎<br />\n<br />\n咁你話有幾多人買佢哋啲裝備<br />\n<br />\n你哋絕對有權利決定自己屌唔屌佢<br />\n<br />\n但係我希望大家唔好再屌<br />\n<br />\n政府一個蛋糕就搞到我哋收皮<br />\n<br />\n咁我哋都真係幾撚廢吓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">不割席、不篤灰、不分化</span><br />\n<br />\n唔係淨係口號<br />\n<br />\n係要實行出嚟㗎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>完</strong></span>"},{"pid":"48cf5d448bfa2492e898c75b6c6fb7490225c98e","tid":1652111,"uid":209543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:35:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12dbdd6586122cc