:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:00:00.000Z","msg":"得喇唔好再出post講隻小學雞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢開咪開，唔開都唔駛又求又奶<br />\n大把人自己科水買返黎再拎去前線<br />\n我寧願你地即刻行動走去撲貨，都好過喺fb ig度氹隻小學雞咁肉酸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n****（借位宣傳）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日七點中環見</span></span><br />\n和勇一家一齊出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多你一個好撚多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gq9iPrf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGq9iPrf.jpg&h=c5742ce7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手洗版呀連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪再喺關鍵時間互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />襯美國議員訪港要集氣畀佢地見證，盡快過香港人權法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632d57113fb8c91c730951665b51e990211b3444","tid":1652111,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e869c5f261f8152aaa2f67b21f167e02c4000ea","tid":1652111,"uid":1187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b076d487eab2ce95b6a1fc5d6e5f3f2157fee16","tid":1652111,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b5771663ed19c0b4c882ed10c7af85a2e8fe50a5","tid":1652111,"uid":1187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:38:37.000Z","msg":"問題係佢態度 佢屌買家係窮閪喎 手足要咁講嘢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fm6Jf2v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFm6Jf2v.png&h=a1756c5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:51:47.000Z","msg":"呢個行為係錯<br />\n但係你係唔係真係要咁樣樣屌佢呢？<br />\n再加上<br />\n你班連登仔而家係屌緊佢小學雞行為喎<br />\n關咩事呢？<br />\n畀著我<br />\n如果我平賣畀你<br />\n你都咁樣屌我<br />\n我都執柒左佢啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:53:34.000Z","msg":"你係咪誤會咗? 無人屌佢加價喎 係屌佢態度喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":